r your eCommerce WordPress Theme. Just image and we bring it be true</li>\n    <li>Unlimited color choices: you can select any color and decorate your site as you want.</li>\n    <li>Unlimited layouts and templates.</li>\n    <li>Self-hosted HTML5 video player.</li>\n    <li>Custom audio player.</li>\n    <li>Google Fonts support (600+):</li>\n    <li>Retina ready: Your Adot eCommerce WordPress Theme with look great in any technique devices</li>\n    <li>Translation ready (.po/.mo files): support Adot eCommerce WordPress Theme to be translated in different languages</li>\n    <li>One click DEMO data importer: simply click a button and then you get Your Adot eCommerce WordPress Theme installed</li>\n    <li>and so much more&#8230;</li>\n</ul>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThimPress/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/face-book.png\" alt=\"eCommerce WordPress Theme - adot - 4\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://twitter.com/thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/twitter.png?v=3\" alt=\"eCommerce WordPress Theme - adot - 5\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+Thimpress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/google.png\" alt=\"eCommerce WordPress Theme - adot - 6\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/user/thimpress\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/follow-Tf.png?v=3\" alt=\"eCommerce WordPress Theme - adot - 7\" /></a> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"item-description__our-premium-wordpress-themes\">WordPress Themes by ThimPress</h3>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034?utm_source=adot&#38;utm_medium=desc\"><img src=\"https://s3.envato.com/files/225684161/01_preview.__large_preview-3.__large_preview.jpg\" alt=\"Education WordPress Theme\" title=\"Education WordPress Theme\" /></a>\n<