(1295, 476, '_lp_key_features', 'a:9:{i:0;s:40:\"Complete Online Course Material Delivery\";i:1;s:40:\"Aligned with Global Brand Certifications\";i:2;s:32:\"Hands on Training with 40+ tools\";i:3;s:26:\"Live and Capstone Projects\";i:4;s:24:\"Online Classes Available\";i:5;s:25:\"Offline Classes Available\";i:6;s:39:\"Online Form Fill up Facility Available.\";i:7;s:20:\"Duration : 12 Months\";i:8;s:80:\"For assistance, Call +91 84818 05615. ( Timing : 11am – 6pm, Thursday Closed )\";}'),
(1296, 476, '_lp_faqs', 'a:7:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:27:\"What is OMCP Certification?\";i:1;s:682:\"The OMCP (Online Marketing Certified Professional) Certification is the industry\'s premier certification for online marketing professionals who have verified experience and have demonstrated the working knowledge of digital marketing concepts and best practices. Requirements for online marketing certification are based on a combination of applied industry experience, education and certification exam results designed by industry thought leaders, experts, renowned authors and educators in the field. Those who wish to pursue the OMCP certification will have demonstrated their knowledge and expertise by fulfilling the requirements by OMCP and their approved training providers. \";}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:41:\"What is Facebook Blueprint Certification?\";i:1;s:298:\"Facebook Blueprint is one of the top and most popular Digital Marketing certifications globally, and proof of advanced-level competency in the digital advertising industry. With this program, you receive a free voucher for taking up the Facebook Blueprint Digital Marketing Associate certification.\";}i:2;a:2:{i:0;s:51:\"How will I earn the Google Analytics Certification?\";i:1;s:409:\"Once you’ve completed the online Digital Marketing course, you’ll need to register on the Google Analytics Academy website. From there, you’ll sign up to take the Google Analytics Qualification Exam, which consists of 70 true/false and multiple-choice questions that must be answered within 90 minutes. To pass the exam, you must receive a minimum score of 80%. The certification is valid for 18 months.\";}i:3;a:2:{i:0;s:45:\"How will I earn the Google Ads Certification?\";i:1;s:379:\"Once you’ve completed this Digital Marketing course, you’ll need to register as a Google Partner. On the Google Partners site, you’ll sign up to take the Google Ads Fundamentals Exam, which consists of 100 multiple choice questions that must be answered within 90 minutes. To pass the exam, you must receive a minimum score of 80%. The certification is valid for 12 months.\";}i:4;a:2:{i:0;s:53:\"How to earn Google\'s Video Advertising Certification?\";i:1;s:328:\"You can earn your Google Video Advertising Certification by passing the Google Video Advertising Assessment and the Google Ads Fundamentals Assessment.\r\nOnce you earn this certification, you will receive a personalized certificate that you can print from your Academy for Ads profile and showcase your expertise in this subject.\";}i:5;a:2:{i:0;s:83:\"What is the Hootsuite Platform Training Course and how will I earn its Certificate?\";i:1;s:358:\"In this module, you’ll develop the skills to use core Hootsuite products to their full potential, boosting the impact of your social media efforts, driving results, and proving your ROI.\r\n\r\nOnce you\'ve completed the Hootsuite Platform Training, you\'ll be ready to take the exam on the Hootsuite Academy website to become a Hootsuite Certified Professional.\";}i:6;a:2:{i:0;s:81:\"What is the HubSpot Platform Training Course and how will I earn its Certificate?\";i:1;s:312:\"This email marketing course will teach you how to create an email marketing strategy that grows your business, and your career.\r\n\r\n\r\nOnce you\'ve completed the HubSpot Email Marketing Certification course, you\'ll be ready to take the exam on the HubSpot Academy website to become a HubSpot Certified Professional.\";}}'),
