(778, 1, '2021-06-04 09:58:59', '2021-06-04 09:58:59', '<strong>Learning Objectives -</strong> In this module, we will understand what PHP &amp;MySQL is and why it is so popular. You will learn PHP basics, installation setup, data types, arrays and decision making statements.\r\n\r\n<strong>Topics -</strong> PHP introduction, Environment setup in different platforms, Script syntax, How to declare variable and data types, Constants, Arrays, Strings, Web concepts, Decision making statements, loop types, operators', 'PHP Basics and Conditional Logic Copy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'php-basics-and-conditional-logic-copy', '', '', '2021-06-04 09:58:59', '2021-06-04 09:58:59', '', 0, 'http://7star/lessons/php-basics-and-conditional-logic-copy/', 0, 'lp_lesson', '', 0);
