>\r\n 	<li>Build multiple digital marketing skills and catapult your career in digital marketing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>A student looking to build a career in one of the most sought-after domains today:</strong>\r\n<em>If you’re looking to build a career in one of the fastest-growing domains in business, digital marketing is a great start. This course will help you:</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n1) Build a strong foundational knowledge of digital marketing and gain hands-on experience in digital marketing\r\n2) Learn how to plan and execute digital marketing campaigns and prepare for fast-paced digital marketing roles in the industry\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>How will I become a Certified Digital Marketing Professional?</strong></span>\r\n\r\n7 Star Academy’s Digital Marketing course is a good stepping stone for experienced digital marketers to expand the depth and breadth of their digital marketing expertise This digital marketing course offers advanced digital marketing concepts across a variety of domains and offers a hands-on learning experience that will help you gain the skills you need to thrive in today’s evolving marketplace. To become a digital marketing associate, follow these three easy steps:\r\n\r\nComplete the 4 modules and the Capstone project, which are designed to provide you with a clear and structured foundation of the digital marketing domain.\r\n\r\nGain real-life experience by completing a wide range of simulations and projects, learning how to use the most important execution tools and formulating your own strategies with the right channel mix.\r\n\r\nOnce you have completed the course, you’ll be prepared to get OMCA certified to validate your domain knowledge and your ability to lead digital marketing efforts in your organization.', 'Digital Marketing Certification Course', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '425-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-18 23:52:35', '2021-06-18 23:52:35',