ation: underline;\"><strong>What are the tools and projects included in this course?</strong></span></h5>\r\n<strong>Digital Marketing Certification</strong> training is incomplete without practical learning. In this course, you will work on four live projects of 10 hours each that will provide you hands-on digital marketing experience.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Project 1: Google Analytics &amp; SEO: You will set up your business website, ensure proper SEO, and enable Google Analytics to analyze its performance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Project 2: Google Ads: You will design a Google Ads campaign to increase relevant paid search traffic to your website.</li>\r\n 	<li>Project 3: Facebook Marketing: You will run a Facebook marketing campaign for your website and maintain the Facebook page to ensure brand visibility and engagement.</li>\r\n 	<li>Project 4:YouTube and Video Marketing: You will run a YouTube marketing campaign for your website and maintain your YouTube channel.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Who is eligible to take this Digital Marketing course?</strong></span></h5>\r\nThe <strong>Digital Marketing Certification</strong> program is ideal for any business professional, marketing consultant or student interested in jump-starting a career in digital marketing, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sales or business professional looking to accelerate your career:</strong>\r\n<em>This program will give you an insider’s view into the digital marketing domain. </em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>An entrepreneur interested in leveraging digital marketing to improve the ROI for your company:</strong>\r\n<em>We live in a digital world where most of your customers live online. So if you’re trying to grow your brand or boost online sales, digital marketing is a critical part of your marketing strategy.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Traditional marketer striving to enhance your knowledge and skills in digital marketing:</strong>\r\n<em>Digital marketing has been gaining prominence over the last few years, and if you’re an expert marketer in traditional channels and methods, then adding digital marketing skills can be a great boost for your career.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Digital marketer hoping to broaden your skillsets and accelerate your career to the next level:</strong>\r\n<em>In today’s business world, digital marketers must be able to wear multiple hats and execute campaigns across different types of marketing channels to stay ahead of the competition.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>A student looking to build a career in one of the most sought-after domains today:</strong>\r\n<em>If you’re looking to build a career in one of the fastest-growing domains in business, <strong>digital marketing certification</strong> is a great start. </em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5 id=\"\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>How will I become a Certified Digital Marketing Professional?</strong></span></h5>\r\n7 Star Academy’s <strong>Digital Marketing Certification</strong> course is a good stepping stone for experienced digital marketers to expand the depth and breadth of their digital marketing expertise This <strong>digital marketing certification</strong> course offers advanced digital marketing concepts across a variety of domains and offers a hands-on learning experience that will help you gain the skills you need to thrive in today’s evolving marketplace. To become a digital marketing associate, follow these three easy steps:\r\n\r\nComplete the 4 modules and the Capstone project, which are designed to provide you with a clear and structured foundation of the digital marketing domain.\r\n\r\nGain real-life experience by completing a wide range of simulations and projects, learning how to use the most important execution tools and formulating your own strategies with the right channel mix.\r\n\r\nOnce you have completed the <strong>digital marketing certification</strong> course, you’ll be prepared to get OMCA certified to validate your domain knowledge and your ability to lead digital marketing efforts in your organization.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Digital Marketing Certification Course', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '425-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-19 01:38:26', '2021-06-19 01:38:26', '', 425, 'http://7star/?p=1269', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
