ams and digital marketing initiatives for your organization\\u003cbr\\u003e4) Understand how digital marketing disciplines all work together and how to optimize your use of each one\",\"visible\":true},{\"id\":\"faq-question-1624147358367\",\"title\":\"Who should take this Online Digital Marketing Diploma Coure?\",\"content\":\"Anyone who is looking to further his or her career in digital marketing should take this digital marketing course, especially those seeking leadership positions. Any of these roles can benefit from this Digital Marketing certification training:\\u003cbr\\u003e1) Marketing Managers\\u003cbr\\u003e2) Digital Marketing Specialists\\u003cbr\\u003e3) Marketing or Sales Professionals\\u003cbr\\u003e4) Management, Engineering, Business, or Communication Graduates\\u003cbr\\u003e5)Entrepreneurs or Business Owners\\u003cbr\\u003e6) Marketing Consultant\",\"visible\":true},{\"id\":\"faq-question-1624147981203\",\"title\":\"How will I earn the \\u003ca href=\\u0022https://www.facebook.com/business/learn/certification\\u0022 target=\\u0022_blank\\u0022 data-type=\\u0022URL\\u0022 data-id=\\u0022https://www.facebook.com/business/learn/certification\\u0022 rel=\\u0022noreferrer noopener\\u0022\\u003eFacebook Blueprint Certification\\u003c/a\\u003e?\",\"content\":\"The Facebook Blueprint certification program is designed to thoroughly assess advanced-level competency in the skills needed to be a successful Facebook advertiser.\\u003cbr\\u003eYou can choose from any of the two types of Blueprint Certification below:\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cspan style=\\u0022text-decoration: underline;\\u0022\\u003eFacebook Certified Planning Professional Certification which consists of:\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e1) Facebook Advertising Core Competencies exam\\u003cbr\\u003e2) Facebook Certified Planning Professional \\u003cbr\\u003e \\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cspan style=\\u0022text-decoration: underline;\\u0022\\u003eFacebook Certified Buying Professional Certification which consists of:\\u003c/span\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e1) Facebook Advertising Core Competencies exam\\u003cbr\\u003e2) Facebook Certified Buying Professional exam\\u003cbr\\u003e \\u003cbr\\u003eYou must complete and pass any of the certification exams with a score of 700 or higher in order to receive your digital badge. You’ll have 75 minutes to pass every exam, which includes 50 to 60 questions each. All Facebook Blueprint certifications remain valid for 12 months, with options to maintain your certification status by demonstrating your ongoing proficiency.\",\"visible\":true},{\"id\":\"faq-question-1624148413237\",\"title\":\"\",\"content\":\"\",\"visible\":true}]} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-rank-math-faq-block\"><div class=\"rank-math-faq-item\"><h3 class=\"rank-math-question\">What are the objectives of this Digital Marketing Diploma Course?</h3><div class=\"rank-math-answer\">This online digital marketing diploma course gives you an in-depth understanding and advanced knowledge of the eight most important digital marketing domains and includes real-world projects and virtual simulations for gaining domain experience. You’ll be exposed to 30 digital marketing tools extensive project experience and Mimic Pro simulations to make you job-ready.<br><br>After you have completed this digital marketing training program, you will receive a digital marketing certificate from 7 Star Academy stating that you have acquired the skill set of a Digital Marketing Specialist, validating your ability to lead digital marketing efforts in your organization.</div></div><div class=\"rank-math-faq-item\"><h3 class=\"rank-math-question\">What skills will you learn in this Digital Marketing Diploma Course?</h3><div class=\"rank-math-answer\">Digital marketing encompasses a range of disciplines, and there is an enormous demand for digital marketers with the right skills. This digital marketing online training provides access to 35+ live instructor-led online classes conducte